making a Flask-based website to serve as a portfolio and contact form for my
cousin's pet-illustration business. Based heavily on the Flask tutorial. 
Will include a contact form/commision request.

To run locally:
  Install virtualenv and run
    . venv/bin/activate
    pip install flask
    ./run

  See the installation guide for more info
    flask.pocoo.org/docs/installation

